          "date": "2013-03-29 22:38:32.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-2789 lod: synchronize access to ldo_stripe(nr)",
        "message": "LU-2789 lod: synchronize access to ldo_stripe(nr)\n\nAdd a semaphore lod_stripe_sem to struct lod_object to synchronize\nassignment to ldo_stripe(nr).  Acquire this semaphore when checking if\nstriping has been loaded for an object (as in the case of setattr()).\nIn lod_ah_init() use ldo_def_stripenr instead of ldo_stripenr to store\nthe stripe count hint and transfer it to ldo_stripenr later in\nlod_qos_prep_create().  This removes LOD's dependence on\ndt_write_lock() the next object to synchronize internally.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I253b4425fe22a46380603d6c17d81d4681fee20a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
